605
00:33:32.387 --> 00:33:35.849
I believe in the justice system.
but it's not perfect.

606
00:33:36.350 --> 00:33:39.810
And when the system fails us.
it's up to us to fix it.

607
00:33:39.811 --> 00:33:41.897
