- Yes.

705
00:40:34.268 --> 00:40:35.394
Yes.

706
00:40:36.270 --> 00:40:37.729
- Sure.
- Sure. Okay?

707
00:40:38.313 --> 00:40:39.648
- [Anna] Hmm.
- [Max] Okay.

708
00:40:43.026 --> 00:40:44.486
